a]]|FRY|144\u2013133|[[Konyaspor|Kombassan Konya]]|TUR|81\u201366|63\u201367|winner=1}}\n{{TwoLegResult|[[Peristeri B.C.|Peristeri 3Bit]]|GRE|151\u2013158|[[Scaligera Basket Verona|Riello Mash Verona]]|ITA|72\u201368|79\u201390|winner=2}}\n{{TwoLegResult|[[Cholet Basket|Cholet]]|FRA|139\u2013124|[[JDA Dijon Basket|JDA Dijon]]|FRA|82\u201362|57\u201362|winner=1}}\n{{TwoLegResult|[[Aris B.C.|Aris Moda Bagno]]|GRE|158\u2013166|[[Pallacanestro Virtus Roma|Calze Pompea Roma]]|ITA|79\u201380|79\u201386|winner=2}}\n|}\n\n==Semi finals==\n{{TwoLeg start}}\n{{TwoLegResult|[[KK Crvena zvezda|Crvena zvezda]]|FRY|155\u2013145|[[Cholet Basket|Cholet]]|FRA|81\u201349|74\u201396|winner=1}}\n{{TwoLegResult|[[Scaligera Basket Verona|Riello Mash Verona]]|ITA|166\u2013154|[[Pallacanestro Virtus Roma|Calze Pompea Roma]]|ITA|96\u201382|70\u201372|winner=1}}\n|}\n\n==Finals==\n{{TwoLeg start}}\n{{TwoLegResult|[[Scaligera Basket Verona|Riello Mash Verona]]|ITA|141\u2013138|[[KK Crvena zvezda|Crvena zvezda]]|FRY|68\u201374|73\u201364|winner=1}}\n|}\n\n{| class=wikitable style=\"text-align:center; margin:auto\"\n!1997\u201398 FIBA Kora\u0107 Cup Champions\n|-\n|{{flagicon|ITA|size=100px}}<br /> '''[[Scaligera Basket Verona|Riello Mash Verona]]''' <br /> '''1st title'''\n|}\n\n== See also ==\n* [[1997\u201398 FIBA EuroLeague]]\n* [[1997\u201398 FIBA EuroCup]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Scaligera Basket Verona 1997\u201398 FIBA Kora\u0107 Cup Winners}}\n{{Kora\u0107 Cup seasons}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Korac Cup}}\n[[Category:FIBA Kora\u0107 Cup|1997-98]]\n[[Category:1997\u201398 in European basketball]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox sports season\n| title               = 1997\u201398 FIBA Kora\u0107 Cup\n| league              = [[FIBA Kora\u0107 Cup]]\n| sport               = Basketball\n| logo                = \n| logo_size           = \n| caption             = \n| duration            = \n| attendance          = \n| season              = \n| season_champs       = \n| MVP                 = \